3.2.1 Periodicity
3.2.1.1 Classification
Elements classified as s, p, d or f block by position in Periodic Table (determined by proton number)
3.2.1.2 Physical Properties of Period 3 Elements
Trends in atomic radius, first ionisation energy and melting point (Na–Ar)
Explain trends in terms of structure and bonding
