Trends in atomic radius, first ionisation energy and melting point (Mg–Ba)
Reactions of Mg–Ba with water
Use of magnesium in extraction of titanium from TiCl₄
Relative solubilities of hydroxides (Mg–Ba): Mg(OH)₂ sparingly soluble → Ba(OH)₂ soluble
